_archive/
.claude/
generate_ai.py
PROMPT.personal.md
screenshot_*.png
*.log

# Playwright MCP scratch output (snapshots, console logs, ad-hoc screenshots)
.playwright-mcp/

# graphify knowledge-graph output (generated artifact — graph.html/json + report)
graphify-out/
